  <name>Todo List</name>
  <summary>A simple and elegant todo list application</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Todo List is a GTK4-based application for managing your daily tasks.
      It features a clean, modern interface following GNOME Human Interface Guidelines.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Add, edit, and delete todo items</li>
      <li>Mark items as completed</li>
      <li>Filter items by status (All/Active/Completed)</li>
      <li>Persistent storage with JSON</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts for quick access</li>
      <li>Beautiful Adwaita theme integration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

